snippet.title: SONIC-el_pendrive_azul
snippet.description:
"Yeah no, I am just at loss of words." (Not Brian2p!)
The story presented here isn't real, this is a fan-made adaptation of a story written by @sinuois, called "El Pendrive Azul" or "El USB Azul"

You can play the game yourself here, but be extremely careful, it contains heavy flashlights: https://gamejolt.com/games/elpendriveazul/883739

Game Engine by @SonicsGamingHub_YT 

Thank you all so much for your support :D
